thread.title: Keith
thread.title_full: The Logo Company reviewed by Keith

author: Keith
title: Keith
text: I am a broadcast consultant and put many new radio stations on the air each year. In the past I have used various logo designers. A couple of years ago one of my General Managers introduced me to The Logo Company. I have launched at least 4 new radio stations with logos from THE LOGO COMPANY. All of those logos look better than anything I could have gotten anywhere else!
